name: InkWord
description: A container for the ink in a word in a paragraph.

properties.name: id
properties.description: Gets the ID of the InkWord object.

properties.name: wordAlternates
properties.description: The words that were recognized in this ink word, in order of likelihood.

properties.name: paragraph
properties.description: The parent paragraph containing the ink word.

properties.name: languageId
properties.description: The id of the recognized language in this ink word.

methods.name: load
methods.description: Fills the proxy object created in JavaScript layer with property and object values specified in the parameter.

parameters.name: param
parameters.description: Accepts parameter and relationship names as delimited string or an array. Or, provide [loadOption](loadoption.md) object.
